43:27.375 --> 43:29.917
I thought her expertise
would be necessary.

43:29.917 --> 43:33.375
‐ Of course.
‐ Thank you.

43:33.375 --> 43:35.708
‐ DEA pharmacologist
David Govin

43:35.708 --> 43:37.583
will now take you
through the data

43:37.583 --> 43:43.083
which was derived
from 1,304 autopsies.

43:44.958 --> 43:46.458
‐ To start off,

43:46.458 --> 43:51.083
