52:56.667 --> 52:58.000
After careful consideration,

52:58.000 --> 53:00.125
I have decided to indict
Michael Friedman,

53:00.125 --> 53:02.958
Paul Goldenheim, and
Howard Udell on felony charges.

53:02.958 --> 53:04.000
Have a great day.

53:09.750 --> 53:12.500
‐ So how is this going to work
if they won't let us indict?

53:17.500 --> 53:19.458
‐ I have no idea.

53:24.333 --> 53:28.375
Hello?

53:28.375 --> 53:32.375
‐ Hey, Grace, it's Betsy.

53:32.375 --> 53:36.167
‐ Hey.
How are you doing?

53:36.167 --> 53:41.042
‐ Oh, I'm‐‐I'm good.

53:41.042 --> 53:46.875
I think I'm finally getting
a handle on all this mess.

53:46.875 --> 53:48.333
‐ Well, that's great.

53:51.292 --> 53:53.917
‐ How's Eureka Springs?
Oh, you'd love it.

53:53.917 --> 53:55.875
It's um‐‐

53:55.875 --> 53:57.500
it's like Oz
for country queers.

54:02.542 --> 54:06.917
‐ I'd‐‐I'd love
to come by sometime.

54:06.917 --> 54:09.167
Oh, yeah, you should.

54:09.167 --> 54:11.250
Ah, it'd be great to see you.

54:11.250 --> 54:14.917
Hey, uh...

54:14.917 --> 54:19.708
do you think that‐‐
maybe that when I'm better...

54:21.875 --> 54:25.042
we could, uh...

54:25.042 --> 54:28.208
try again?

54:28.208 --> 54:29.792
Start over?

54:31.875 --> 54:35.375
‐ Um...

54:35.375 --> 54:38.375
I don't think
that would work.

54:38.375 --> 54:42.167
But, uh,
I'd sure love to be friends.

54:51.333 --> 54:55.458
‐ Yeah.
I‐‐

54:55.458 --> 54:56.750
I understand.

54:59.125 --> 55:01.083
Be real nice to be friends.

55:05.542 --> 55:08.083
Uh...

55:08.083 --> 55:10.542
take care, Grace.

55:10.542 --> 55:12.417
‐ You too, Bets.

55:36.208 --> 55:39.000
It's been a while
since I've seen you.

55:39.000 --> 55:44.125
‐ Yeah, well, I'm starting
Suboxone tomorrow.

55:44.125 --> 55:48.833
So...give me one hell
of a sendoff.

55:48.833 --> 55:50.375
You got it.

57:34.667 --> 57:37.458
‐ I'm so sorry, Diane.
I'm so sorry.

58:30.833 --> 58:32.250
Hello?

58:32.250 --> 58:38.292
‐ Hey, Diane, it's Sam Finnix.
I'm just waiting here.

58:38.292 --> 58:40.625
You and Betsy
are still coming, right?

58:42.833 --> 58:46.625
I'm sorry,
but Betsy's in heaven now.

58:50.958 --> 58:53.125
My girl is finally out
of her pain.

58:54.208 --> 58:55.667
‐ That‐‐

59:24.542 --> 59:27.542
New medicines
are changing the world.

59:27.542 --> 59:31.375
They can cure diseases
once thought incurable.

59:31.375 --> 59:33.542
They can bring joy...

59:33.542 --> 59:36.250
where there was
once only pain.

59:36.250 --> 59:40.625
It has truly been an honor to
testify before this committee

59:40.625 --> 59:45.292
on a subject that means
so much to me and my family.

59:45.292 --> 59:48.833
And I'd like to leave you with
one very important thought.

59:51.000 --> 59:54.708
No laws or regulations

59:54.708 --> 59:59.875
will ever be able
to stop the miracle

59:59.875 --> 1:00:02.083
that is modern pharmaceuticals.

1:00:04.250 --> 1:00:05.792
Thank you.

1:00:11.208 --> 1:00:13.625
The record speaks for itself.
